Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:06.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:06.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:12.66,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:12.66,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:33.61,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:33.61,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.08,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.08,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:44.59,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:44.59,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:50.13,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:50.13,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:56.37,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:56.37,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:01.67,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:01.67,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:07.38,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:07.38,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:11.22,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:11.22,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.87,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:35.66,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This summer and last winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:44.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't go back home, using work and homework as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:47.21,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Station: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Kumagaya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still only at Kumagaya, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's an hour to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:57.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange sense of distance always proves\Nto be an obstacle on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:01:59.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:02.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Yuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... You should stop by more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been? How's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten used to living by yourself yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, have you seen my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:17.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she collapsed last night because she was overworked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:21.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She pushed herself since it's the end of the year and we lack staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-san should be nursing her back at home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kazu-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:32.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you haven't been coming\Nhome because you don't like Kazu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:34.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you talked to him about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-san's a pretty nice guy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:40.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He may have a loud voice and his feet may be a bit smelly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:41.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's nice on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:44.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right! You should go talk to him about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:47.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's not that I don't like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just really busy with work and homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been back for half a year already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't those just excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I just lost half of my HP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:06.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My father passed away from an illness when\NI was still in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:13.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a weak body. He was tall and skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He had big hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:19.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And he had a gentle smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.89,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,0)\fscx70\1a&H64&\fs27\fry-10\bord0\shad0\i1\pos(440,62)\c&H615D58&}Takemoto-sama{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On his last day, in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:30.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With his large yet slender hands, he grasped mine with unbelievable strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.28,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of your mother for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:38.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never forget the warmth and strength\Nthat passed through his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have to help Mom."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"We have to be happy together."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:50.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have to study hard and find a job close to home, so\NI can buy a house where we'll live together one day."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:53.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But around the end of my second year of high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Aida Kazuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:05.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The man my mother brought with her was\Nthe complete opposite of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:11.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I shook his calloused hand, I absentmindedly thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:16.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah, so Mom picked a strong person this time."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:20.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to only worry about me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can start thinking about yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:28.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that, for the first time in my life,\NI realized that I was empty inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:35.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until that point, I was blindfolding myself to many\Nthings because I had to "take care of my mother."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:40.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I was suddenly free to do whatever I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:45.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to face the fact that I couldn't really do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:50.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know a single thing that I was good at...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:54.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I was able to convince myself that\NI liked making things with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Relying on that alone, I left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The factory is still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother didn't like that zinc factory because\Nshe thought it polluted the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:13.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But my father and I liked to watch it light\Nup all over the mountain in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were waving your hands like this just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,K-K-K-K-Kazu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:26.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:31.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you seemed to be taking your time,\Nand we couldn't reach you by phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so Mitsu-san thought you might be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really has been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:43.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, want to go somewhere with me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:48.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to the batting center for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Bat your heart out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.12,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs50\fsp-3\i1\bord0.1\shad0\be1\frz20\pos(386,187)\c&H9F855E&\3c&H6C5335&}1 game 300 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a little too into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:05.72,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Don't tell me that you haven't been coming\Nhome because you don't like Kazu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.06,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She was right on the dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm going to go for the home run prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.23,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little uncomfortable with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:19.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:21.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hit it straight ahead this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.66,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.08,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really uncomfortable with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why haven't you been coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.25,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I also don't like this side of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:41.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsu-san will be lonely if you don't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when she's lonely, I'm sad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:46.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she has you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can replace someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:59.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I tried to make Mitsu-san happy\Nin the stead of her late husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that didn't turn out too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:06.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't replace Yuuichi-san in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:12.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned the hard way that you can't just replace family members.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:19.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that all I could do was work hard and stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want you to do what you can from your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm uncomfortable with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:37.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I always choose my words carefully and often just keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:41.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how clumsy or uncool this person is with his words...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:45.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been able to get his feelings across with driving effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and sweep my mother off her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:53.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come home more often!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Home run
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've seen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this music?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hit a home run, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:14.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so lame... So corny... It's such corny music!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:36.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her bedside was accompanied by various little\Nitems that Kazu-san had lined up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:42.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably what Kazu-san meant\Nby "I'll work hard and stay by her side."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you grown again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:11.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say anything more and just kept holding on to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.62,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of your mother for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Even though I promised him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.76,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\shad0\bord0\1a&H64&\b1\an8\frz-15\c&H4D4944&\t(0,5000,\fs33)\move(371,63,371,60}Takasaki Station
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:34.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back more often, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well then, I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep studying hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a loud voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to call!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm uncomfortable with him just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:48.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't forget to eat your greens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:50.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always so straightforward and honest\Nwith his words, and a little rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't lose faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But kind at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Keep working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:52.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll keep cheering for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so bright that I don't think I'm a match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:58.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:02.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess everyone's still at their homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.10,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Attention Takemoto! {\be1\3c&H000000&}Come to the Hanamoto's right now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:19.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's a super huge nozawana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:21.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:23.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my otoshidama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:25.19,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Otoshidama: {\be1\3c&H000000&}monetary gift that Japanese children\Nget from relatives on New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:25.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring any.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:29.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this one right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I open this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we just open everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please start with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't eat too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or you'll be too full to eat anything once we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:52.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:57.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At least they responded...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:58.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibi-Moni wants to go to the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Chibi-Moni!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you just want to go yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:18.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The tickets that Morita-san brought\Nfor the Christmas gift exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:19.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,300,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was only 1,000 yen worth of tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's as expected of Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:29.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fiendishly lucky when it comes to money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:31.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:36.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We won! That Christmas lottery ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! My money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:44.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll be seeing you in court!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to hire a lawyer for only 300,000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's all go on a trip! How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.29,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I ended up having to pay for all six of us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.33,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, am I just here as the driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.25,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, the 300,000 got used up all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it's all right. Hagu seems to be having fun, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:18.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, don't open packs of snacks one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you shouldn't leave crumbs everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:24.06,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho! So there's a normal person in this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:27.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei will have to clean up this rental car before we return it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:28.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes'm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we all clean up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:33.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:36.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san is coming straight to the inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:40.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on a trip, but for it to be on the\Nsame day as his employment exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:41.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:49.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's surprising that lazy Mayama is willing\Nto switch trains to come all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:53.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to follow his own agenda but hates being left out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama is basically just a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:00.89,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.10,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She likes Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:13.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tamura-sensei said that you should come get your work\Nsince he's cleaning up the photography room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. I'll go later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:19.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. You're always putting things off until later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your photographs will get thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, then whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:27.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own work. Make sure you get it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:29.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say I didn't warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:42.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of it, he won't be coming back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Mayama is going, Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:46.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:52.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, there's only one person in this\Nworld who can make Mayama run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:58.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:06.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is for the person I like the most to like me the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If feels like it'll never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever... Like this, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:19.26,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\shad0\frz3\pos(319,415)\c&H595854&\3c&HDCDFDE&}Directory of the Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:19.38,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\shad0\frz6\pos(308,401)\3c&HDCDFDE&\c&H595854&}Directory of the Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:19.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\shad0\frz8\pos(293,387)\3c&HDCDFDE&\c&H595854&}Directory of the Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:19.63,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\shad0\frz11\pos(283,374)\3c&HDCDFDE&\c&H595854&}Directory of the Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:20.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\shad0\frz13\pos(269,361)\3c&HDCDFDE&\c&H595854&}Directory of the Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This place has four baths!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This yukata is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:27.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A lacquer lipped bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:32.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about them being so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:34.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Today is a weekday, so\Nwe don't have too many customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they all your relatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be tough for Daddy to handle them all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my students at college!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still single!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs sure are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:15:01.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner is at 5:30, so can you gather everyone in the men's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.34,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\fad(0,300)\an7\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&\pos(690,34)}Yamada-sama\NHanamoto-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.97,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\fs23\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&\pos(616,30)}Wisteria Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.39,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs24\an7\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&\pos(309,69)}Hanamoto-sama\NMorita-sama\NMayama-sama\NTakemoto-sama\N{\be1\3c&H000000&}({\c&H536FAE&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1}Men's Room{\be1\3c&H000000&\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.7})
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.39,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs24\an7\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&\pos(160,34)}Madder Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san sure is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, Morita...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing? That thing looks expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:27.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness that this is only a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:29.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're gonna get scolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can draw a replacement and put it in its place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw? With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:40.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He drew a morotai with soy sauce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.73,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Morotai (dim style): {\be1\3c&H000000&}a style of Japanese drawing with hazy, unclear shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, give it to me. Give me that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:58.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come apologize with me if I draw one more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Can I do it on the back of February?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do a landscape?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:04.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:13.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! How can I preserve a soy sauce picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:13.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I draw next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A spiny lobster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:23.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san, you have to start with "He loves\Nme not!" when doing it with a crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. They're totally drunk already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How was your employment exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san, you've only been applying\Nto top-notch jobs, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you only applying to such seemingly impossible places?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:40.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:47.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In this day and age... I told him to apply\Nto more down-to-earth places, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I applied to those places precisely because of this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to try and fail, you might\Nas well do it with a high goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:17:02.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"You just chose impossible places so that you could\Nfail them all and stick around at Rika-san's"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what Yamada is saying in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go take another bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, enough of those employment exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just start a company together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become really wealthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, Morita-san, your head...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have the crab attached to your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, don't be so rowdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Team up with me! Then you'll be No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your seat as the Vice President is already waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:35.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to be No. 2?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:39.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make me happy at all to be No. 2 in a company of two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Hanamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take another bath before we go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:59.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mayama-san. The outdoor bath was really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:04.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it seems I caught a cold at the exam site.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be better if I lie down for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:13.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:16.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open until 1 AM, so you can just go later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
