Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I being paranoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:19:02.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama-kun. My after-bath snack\Nis always fruity milk and ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:08.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay for you to buy me all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:17.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:20.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, Mayama-san, Hagu-chan won't stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:24.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu sure is cute, even when she's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.82,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of remember seeing something like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Beautiful breasts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.41,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFluid-Light\shad0\bord0\fs80\fscy80\fad(300,300)\pos(434,96)\1a&H32&\c&H333730&}Beautiful breasts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:46.63,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So she has beautiful breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:54.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well, you'll also be like that when you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you also crying, Morita-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:00.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her tears are infectious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:06.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, order more beer already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Make sure you put on your blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. She's so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the men are all that are left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:22.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother. We can just leave them on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:25.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't taken a bath yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:37.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:40.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're getting a job, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:45.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you decide on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide where you want to work on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:04.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For my last memory as a student to be in a bath alone with my\Nprofessor from school... What do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:09.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about things like that, Mayama.\NYou're just making the situation more pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
